      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10791"> </a>Hold the oil pump (1) in a vice taking care not to damage the drive gear (2).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_000701711.jpg"></center>
