      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10796"> </a>Make sure that vice jaws are faced with soft material.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10799"> </a>Remove the plug (3) and extract the spring (4) and by-pass valve (5).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_059103011.jpg"></center>
      </div>
